FBIS4-33327 "drlat108_j_94008" FBIS-LAT-94-108 Daily Report 4 Jun 1994 Panama IDB Confirms Not Lending Panama $270 Million IDB Confirms Not Lending Panama $270 Million PA0606043994 Panama City Circuito RPC Television in Spanish 1730 GMT 4 Jun 94 PA0606043994 Panama City Circuito RPC Television Spanish BFN [From the "Day to Day" newscast] [Text] The Inter-American Development Bank [IDB] today confirmed that it will not be able to lend Panama $270 million for investments, because public enterprises have not been privatized, nor have they reduced their expenses.
